summary: Laura Piel is President and founder of Renaissance Personnel Group, a full service recruiting and staffing firm that has served businesses in Arizona since 1994. Renaissance manages and supplies skilled people in administrative, technical and professional disciplines in the Phoenix Metropolitan area, and we offer a full spectrum of workforce solutions including contract, temporary and direct hire placement. People are three-dimensional; jobs are multifaceted; and the needs of a business team complex. We explore more than the job description and we look beyond the resume to match people and culture. At Renaissance we never lose sight of what we do best: Making lives and workplaces better. • Established in 1994• Tenured Staff operates with a Collaborative Approach to Candidate Selection and Placement• 94% Placement Success Rate• Comprehensive Client Base• Extensive Passive Candidate Network with High Rate of Referral• Behavioral Assessments to aid in Employee Selection and Team BuildingSpecialties: Digital Media, Interactive Marketing, Product Manager,  Marketing Manager, Marketing Director, .Net Developers, Oracle, SQL DBA, Project Manager, Analysts, Financial Analyst, Accountant, Controller, Programmers, Business Development, Executive Assistant, Administrative Assistant, Recruiter, Web Designer, Web Developer, Instructional Design.
